1
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,319
Cuckoo, cuckoo

2
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:43,280
Cuckoo, cuckoo

3
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:51,480
Cuckoo, cuckoo

4
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,439
What are you standing there for?

5
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,519
The bridal sedan chair

6
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,959
took Xiu Gu away.

7
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:05,840
Impossible.

8
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,599
Xiu Gu wouldn't go to the Huo family.

9
00:02:13,239 --> 00:02:14,480
She was taken by force.

10
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,279
Xiu Gu!

11
00:02:25,239 --> 00:02:26,320
Xiu Gu!

12
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,040
Xiu Gu!

13
00:02:29,119 --> 00:02:30,080
What are you shouting for?

14
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,600
Tell that Huo guy to come out!

15
00:02:31,999 --> 00:02:32,999
Xiu Gu!

16
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:37,999
Fat Uncle.

17
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:41,080
What brings you to my door?

18
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,999
You're like a fly gathering honey,

19
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,440
playing dumb, aren't you?

20
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,360
Where have you hidden Xiu Gu?

21
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,200
Tell her to come out!

22
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,160
Hold on, hold on.

23
00:02:48,799 --> 00:02:51,839
I brought Xiu Gu home as my lawfully wedded wife.

24
00:02:52,519 --> 00:02:54,480
Now you're at my door,

25
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,480
looking for my wife.

26
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,839
That's a bit unreasonable, isn't it?

27
00:03:02,839 --> 00:03:03,799
Second floor of the winery.

28
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,959
What second floor?

29
00:03:08,839 --> 00:03:10,160
You saw it all, didn't you?

30
00:03:10,399 --> 00:03:11,239
Saw what?

31
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,080
I didn't see anything.

32
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,239
Xiu Gu

33
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,440
would never marry you.

34
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,200
This man,

35
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,920
he has feelings for Xiu Gu.

36
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,040
I can understand that.

37
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,799
After all, Xiu Gu is a good woman.

38
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:24,519
Otherwise,

39
00:03:24,519 --> 00:03:26,360
I wouldn't have liked her for so long either.

40
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:26,920
Right?

41
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:28,160
Exactly.

42
00:03:28,399 --> 00:03:29,119
Everyone knows

43
00:03:29,119 --> 00:03:30,679
Xiu Gu is your savior.

44
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,399
How can you harbor

45
00:03:32,399 --> 00:03:33,760
covetous thoughts toward your savior?

46
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,999
Xiu Gu is my childhood betrothed.

47
00:03:36,399 --> 00:03:38,399
Only I can give her a good life.

48
00:03:38,799 --> 00:03:40,200
You've only been here a few days.

49
00:03:40,399 --> 00:03:42,119
So I'm warning you.

50
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:44,880
If you keep pestering my Xiu Gu,

51
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,839
I won't be polite.

52
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,480
This man is unreasonable.

53
00:03:48,799 --> 00:03:49,360
Tell him to leave.

54
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,320
Go, leave.

55
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,160
It's very simple.

56
00:03:51,559 --> 00:03:53,920
Call Xiu Gu out to say it to my face.

57
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,160
You're being pestering and unreasonable.

58
00:03:55,239 --> 00:03:55,640
See him out.

59
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:56,119
Stop right there.

60
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,519
What do you want to do?

61
00:03:59,679 --> 00:04:00,559
Or else?

62
00:04:00,679 --> 00:04:01,959
Or else what will you do?

63
00:04:03,839 --> 00:04:05,880
Fists have no eyes.

64
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:13,799
Stand back.

65
00:04:14,399 --> 00:04:14,920
Stand back.

66
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:26,680
Go.

67
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:27,919
Stand back.

68
00:04:28,599 --> 00:04:29,240
Back out.

69
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:31,839
Back up.

70
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:34,839
Keep backing up.

71
00:04:37,039 --> 00:04:38,279
This is bullying!

72
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,240
What is going on here?

73
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,399
Nothing, it's nothing.

74
00:04:47,039 --> 00:04:49,359
My relative, we have a little conflict.

75
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,440
Commander Qin knows about it.

76
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,039
I won't cause trouble for him.

77
00:04:58,479 --> 00:04:59,680
That's enough.

78
00:05:00,039 --> 00:05:00,919
Bandits raided the prison.

79
00:05:01,039 --> 00:05:02,640
Commander Qin is furious right now.

80
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,760
Don't cause extra trouble here.

81
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:06,359
Understood.

82
00:05:08,039 --> 00:05:08,959
Break it up, break it up.

83
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,120
Break it up, move along.

84
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,640
If you don't release Xiu Gu,

85
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,959
I'm not leaving.

86
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,279
Suit yourself then.

87
00:05:20,919 --> 00:05:22,399
You just wait here.

88
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,159
Let's see if you can fly to the sky

89
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,359
or burrow into the earth.

90
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,440
Close the door.

91
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,440
I'm not leaving!

92
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:01,120
Our Qionglai Town intestine noodles,

93
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,320
outsiders usually don't get to eat them.

94
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:16,760
Smells so good.

95
00:07:18,359 --> 00:07:19,839
Don't talk while eating noodles.

96
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,080
You might choke to death.

97
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,760
Choking is better than starving.

98
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:25,919
I'm not leaving.

99
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,560
I'll find something to eat later.

100
00:07:30,039 --> 00:07:31,279
I'll wait you out.

101
00:08:16,919 --> 00:08:18,240
Cinnamon stimulates the appetite

102
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:22,080
Star anise enhances the fragrance

103
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,159
The spice is just right

104
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,240
I'm even hungrier now

105
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,680
You have hot and sour noodles

106
00:08:44,599 --> 00:08:45,920
I have soup to drink

107
00:08:52,999 --> 00:08:53,759
Why does it smell so good?

108
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,599
It smells pretty good, huh?

109
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:56,839
Let's have a pitch-in meal

110
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,200
How do we do that?

111
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,920
I'll provide the soup and stove

112
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,759
Your rotten vegetable leaves...

113
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,599
...we cook and eat together

114
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,400
You don't say

115
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:08,800
My belly is getting hungry now

116
00:09:09,479 --> 00:09:11,080
Tell you what, I'll be generous

117
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,800
Bring all the leftover veggies to cook

118
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,160
Bring the good ones too

119
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:14,920
Cook them all up

120
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:16,040
Come on, come on

121
00:09:16,119 --> 00:09:17,119
Hurry up, hurry up, hurry up

122
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,479
Hungry

123
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,359
We're all hungry

124
00:09:19,359 --> 00:09:19,839
Deal

125
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,599
Brother, what is this?

126
00:09:30,599 --> 00:09:31,359
Beef offal

127
00:09:31,639 --> 00:09:32,280
Want to buy some?

128
00:09:32,479 --> 00:09:33,400
I'm not buying, I'm not buying

129
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,320
Then forget it

130
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:39,080
What is that? It smells so good

131
00:09:41,119 --> 00:09:42,920
How about a pitch-in meal?

132
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,119
How do we do a pitch-in meal?

133
00:09:46,119 --> 00:09:47,879
I provide the soup, pot, and stove

134
00:09:48,359 --> 00:09:49,320
And the tables and benches

135
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,680
You just provide the beef offal

136
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:51,599
We eat together

137
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,080
Sure

138
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,320
My belly is hungry anyway

139
00:09:55,839 --> 00:09:56,920
Come on, come on

140
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:58,839
Let's eat meat!

141
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:04,759
The soup is fragrant, no tummy trouble

142
00:10:04,839 --> 00:10:05,839
I'll provide the loach

143
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,800
Herbs are nourishing, just missing tripe

144
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:09,920
I'll provide the tripe

145
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:12,639
Chicken, duck, fish, meat, anything goes

146
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:14,239
Anything goes

147
00:10:14,239 --> 00:10:16,959
Radish, blood curd, and tofu

148
00:10:16,959 --> 00:10:19,800
Eat tofu, eat tofu

149
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:22,520
Pitch-in meal, sit in a circle

150
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,639
Contribute more...

151
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,040
...eat more

152
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:26,080
Contribute less...

153
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,520
...still get full

154
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:30,599
Contribute nothing, sit comfortably too

155
00:10:30,599 --> 00:10:32,200
That's right

156
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:38,040
Come on, come on

157
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,639
Cook it up, cook it up

158
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:44,680
Who are you looking for?

159
00:10:47,719 --> 00:10:48,479
Come, come

160
00:10:49,599 --> 00:10:50,239
Come here

161
00:10:50,719 --> 00:10:51,200
Sit

162
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,999
Is your Young Mistress in?

163
00:10:54,359 --> 00:10:55,400
Who are you?

164
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,280
None of your business who I am

165
00:10:57,359 --> 00:10:58,680
I'm just looking for your Young Mistress

166
00:11:00,119 --> 00:11:02,080
Our Eldest Young Master hasn't been gone long

167
00:11:02,479 --> 00:11:04,400
And you dare hit on our Young Mistress?

168
00:11:04,719 --> 00:11:06,040
Qin Dahan... Qin...

169
00:11:06,599 --> 00:11:07,959
What are you talking about?

170
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,719
I'm here to deliver something

171
00:11:11,239 --> 00:11:12,440
A jar of Qiong wine

172
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,719
Here, take it, take it

173
00:11:14,839 --> 00:11:15,920
There's this chubby guy

174
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,639
Told me to give this letter to your Young Mistress

175
00:11:18,839 --> 00:11:19,719
I opened it and took a look

176
00:11:19,719 --> 00:11:20,719
But I didn't understand it

177
00:11:20,959 --> 00:11:21,959
He repeatedly warned me...

178
00:11:21,959 --> 00:11:23,320
...not to give it to your Old Master

179
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,320
You don't look like the Old Master anyway

180
00:11:25,599 --> 00:11:26,080
Take it

181
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:29,599
Stool... Snail... Sound...

182
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,599
Young Mistress

183
00:11:31,959 --> 00:11:32,959
Eldest Young Master

184
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,359
Where is that chubby guy now?

185
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,359
You mean the chubby guy?

186
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:40,639
Where is the chubby guy...

187
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,200
I'm asking you!

188
00:11:42,839 --> 00:11:44,200
Don't rush, don't rush, let me think

189
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,080
I remember now

190
00:11:51,359 --> 00:11:51,839
Where?

191
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,359
I came out to buy meat

192
00:11:53,479 --> 00:11:54,160
I paid the money

193
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,680
He hasn't given me the meat yet!

194
00:11:57,839 --> 00:11:59,520
I haven't finished talking, why run?

195
00:12:27,759 --> 00:12:28,599
Since you're already here...

196
00:12:29,959 --> 00:12:31,359
Stay for lunch before you go.

197
00:12:33,959 --> 00:12:34,759
Forget it.

198
00:12:38,239 --> 00:12:40,040
About this marriage...

199
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,560
I really don't understand it.

200
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,160
Before the wedding,

201
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:47,040
everything was exactly as it should be.

202
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,839
But after she crossed the threshold,

203
00:12:50,879 --> 00:12:53,599
I'm the Huo family's father-in-law, aren't I?

204
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,440
How did things end up like this?

205
00:12:57,839 --> 00:12:59,400
It's been days now.

206
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:01,879
I haven't stepped away from here once.

207
00:13:02,239 --> 00:13:03,920
Xiu Gu has never come out.

208
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,560
Whether she's doing well or not in there,

209
00:13:06,959 --> 00:13:07,719
nobody knows.

210
00:13:08,999 --> 00:13:10,479
Why wouldn't she be doing well?

211
00:13:11,359 --> 00:13:13,879
My son-in-law has always treated her fine.

212
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,560
They grew up together.

213
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:19,440
Young Master Huo has been sensible since childhood.

214
00:13:19,479 --> 00:13:20,800
I don't think it's come to that.

215
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,599
I don't want to talk to you about this.

216
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,959
When I rescue Xiu Gu later,

217
00:13:25,359 --> 00:13:26,639
I'll have her tell you herself.

218
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:28,239
Rescue?

219
00:13:29,839 --> 00:13:31,599
Why would you need to "rescue" her?

220
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:35,999
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

221
00:13:36,239 --> 00:13:39,320
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

222
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,639
What is going on here?

223
00:13:40,639 --> 00:13:42,160
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

224
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,719
These people are here for a pitch-in meal with me.

225
00:13:43,719 --> 00:13:44,719
We're having hotpot.

226
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:47,479
They brought their own meat and vegetables.

227
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,479
Some even brought me wine.

228
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,479
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

229
00:13:51,479 --> 00:13:53,320
Since I'm stuck waiting here anyway,

230
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,239
anyone who wants to join the pitch-in meal

231
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,400
has to shout this slogan.

232
00:13:58,560 --> 00:14:01,479
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

233
00:14:01,719 --> 00:14:04,440
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

234
00:14:04,599 --> 00:14:06,320
A beggar from out of town

235
00:14:06,959 --> 00:14:08,280
dares to come to our Huo family turf

236
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,599
and shame the Huo family name?

237
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,839
Is he some giant snake we can't pin down?

238
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,479
When he's done making a scene,

239
00:14:15,599 --> 00:14:16,520
we'll just spend a little money

240
00:14:16,759 --> 00:14:19,080
and have Commander Qin charge him with disturbing the peace.

241
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,160
Let him learn that

242
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,999
our Young Master is red-hot iron—

243
00:14:21,999 --> 00:14:22,879
you can't even touch him.

244
00:14:23,119 --> 00:14:24,160
That hits the spot!

245
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:27,040
Let him make a scene.

246
00:14:27,479 --> 00:14:27,999
It's ready!

247
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:29,400
Come on in for the pitch-in meal!

248
00:14:29,479 --> 00:14:31,359
Come on, come on!

249
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:33,440
Come on, come on!

250
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:36,160
Come on, come on!

251
00:14:36,239 --> 00:14:37,520
You're really something.

252
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,479
With the crowd you draw,

253
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,160
if you turned this into a business,

254
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,160
you'd make a fortune.

255
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,320
Exactly.

256
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,080
Boss Dong,

257
00:14:44,639 --> 00:14:46,719
this might be more profitable than selling wine!

258
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:47,759
Right, right, right.

259
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,119
If you take your wine

260
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,200
and sell it here,

261
00:14:50,359 --> 00:14:51,639
you'll definitely make more money.

262
00:14:52,959 --> 00:14:53,479
Boss Dong,

263
00:14:53,719 --> 00:14:54,839
this shop is yours, right?

264
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:00,639
Why don't you give it a name?

265
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:01,719
That's right!

266
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:03,959
Alright, alright.

267
00:15:04,639 --> 00:15:05,680
Look here,

268
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,680
we've all gathered here

269
00:15:07,759 --> 00:15:08,920
for the love of good food.

270
00:15:09,599 --> 00:15:11,359
Let's call it "Gourmet Gathering."

271
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:12,719
Gourmet Gathering?

272
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:13,719
Sounds good, sounds good!

273
00:15:14,599 --> 00:15:15,160
Hold on.

274
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:16,920
My surname is Dong.

275
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:20,400
So let's call it "Dongshihui."

276
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,920
Great, great, great!

277
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,400
That works, that works!

278
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:27,119
Dongshihui! Dongshihui! Dongshihui!

279
00:15:27,599 --> 00:15:28,160
Let's eat, let's eat!

280
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,920
Come on down.

281
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:40,920
Hurry!

282
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:46,479
Over there.

283
00:15:47,839 --> 00:15:48,999
What do you mean?

284
00:15:49,239 --> 00:15:50,320
We start from there...

285
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:52,639
...and dig a tunnel to the Huo house.

286
00:15:53,959 --> 00:15:54,839
Dig our way through.

287
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:57,040
That's a bit extreme.

288
00:15:57,119 --> 00:15:58,440
Do you want to see Xiu Gu or not?

289
00:15:59,359 --> 00:16:00,040
Of course.

290
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,999
They won't let us see her.

291
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,839
Don't you think that's strange?

292
00:16:05,119 --> 00:16:06,680
If we don't dig through from here...

293
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:07,520
...and find Xiu Gu...

294
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,560
...how will you know...

295
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:10,800
...if she's safe...

296
00:16:10,959 --> 00:16:12,239
...or dead or alive?

297
00:16:16,359 --> 00:16:18,160
Just the two of us?

298
00:16:19,879 --> 00:16:21,839
Don't you have a better plan?

299
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:26,759
The two of us

300
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:28,879
Eat hotpot by day

301
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,999
Dig holes by night

302
00:16:32,839 --> 00:16:35,080
Fortune telling! Marriage divination!

303
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:38,320
No charge if it's not accurate!

304
00:16:39,239 --> 00:16:39,719
Miss

305
00:16:39,879 --> 00:16:40,959
Your cheeks are flushed like rosy clouds

306
00:16:40,959 --> 00:16:42,160
You're about to get lucky in love

307
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,080
Let me read your fortune

308
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:44,999
You creep

309
00:16:44,999 --> 00:16:45,719
Don't go

310
00:16:45,719 --> 00:16:47,320
That hotpot place is interesting

311
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,719
The shop is a dump, but the taste is amazing

312
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:50,440
Indeed

313
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:51,560
I heard that chubby boss

314
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:52,680
Made a weird rule

315
00:16:52,959 --> 00:16:54,520
Whoever shouts "Come out, come out"

316
00:16:54,759 --> 00:16:55,680
Gets a twenty percent discount

317
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:57,920
Is the boss's surname Sha?

318
00:16:58,759 --> 00:16:59,959
Who has the surname Sha?

319
00:16:59,959 --> 00:17:01,359
It's because he charges so little

320
00:17:01,359 --> 00:17:02,520
He doesn't make any money at all

321
00:17:02,719 --> 00:17:03,959
And he looks short and dumpy

322
00:17:03,959 --> 00:17:05,719
So people call him Boss Sha behind his back

323
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,879
Then why open a hotpot place if not to make money?

324
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:09,800
Who knows?

325
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:11,240
Maybe he has his own plans

326
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:13,280
Excuse me

327
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:15,399
Where is this hotpot place you mentioned?

328
00:17:16,159 --> 00:17:17,760
Up ahead. Dongshihui

329
00:17:19,679 --> 00:17:21,960
We really want to take you as our master

330
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:24,879
I just run this hotpot place for fun

331
00:17:25,320 --> 00:17:26,080
I'm not taking apprentices. No, no

332
00:17:26,639 --> 00:17:28,080
Not bad at all

333
00:17:29,879 --> 00:17:30,760
When did you get here?

334
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,280
You're everywhere

335
00:17:32,919 --> 00:17:34,199
I divined where you were

336
00:17:34,839 --> 00:17:36,040
Just accept us

337
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,879
We sincerely want to learn your craft

338
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:41,000
This lousy hotpot

339
00:17:41,399 --> 00:17:43,520
Doesn't require any craft

340
00:17:43,639 --> 00:17:45,159
I can't learn anything too difficult either

341
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:48,040
We just want a skill to make a living

342
00:17:49,359 --> 00:17:50,119
Well

343
00:17:50,359 --> 00:17:51,879
It's not impossible

344
00:17:53,159 --> 00:17:53,800
Alright, alright

345
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:56,599
This hotpot looks simple

346
00:17:56,599 --> 00:17:57,359
But if you want to make it

347
00:17:57,359 --> 00:17:59,520
Numbing, spicy, fresh, fragrant, and not drying

348
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:00,240
That is very hard

349
00:18:00,439 --> 00:18:01,480
The secret recipe inside

350
00:18:01,599 --> 00:18:03,599
Isn't something you can figure out quickly

351
00:18:04,839 --> 00:18:06,159
There is no secret recipe

352
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,280
Just added some herbs

353
00:18:08,879 --> 00:18:09,560
Not worth much

354
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:11,359
Right, not worth much

355
00:18:11,679 --> 00:18:12,599
But why is it that you

356
00:18:12,599 --> 00:18:14,159
Can't recreate this flavor?

357
00:18:16,439 --> 00:18:19,520
Chinese medicine has a hundred flavors; the difficulty is in the balance

358
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:20,879
The ins and outs of this

359
00:18:20,879 --> 00:18:23,320
Are profound. There's plenty for you to learn

360
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:25,439
Hurry up and call him Master

361
00:18:25,639 --> 00:18:26,560
Master

362
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:28,080
That's right

363
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:29,520
It's almost mealtime

364
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:31,040
Go inside and find something to do

365
00:18:31,879 --> 00:18:32,359
Go in, go in

366
00:18:32,359 --> 00:18:32,760
Okay

367
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:38,240
You with the yellow teeth, faking expertise

368
00:18:38,639 --> 00:18:40,080
Coming here to cause trouble?

369
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:42,480
I'm helping you

370
00:18:43,119 --> 00:18:44,399
Don't you think this is a business opportunity?

371
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:45,439
Well

372
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:47,800
Think about it

373
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:50,040
Once you teach the apprentices

374
00:18:50,280 --> 00:18:51,119
You can open branches

375
00:18:51,599 --> 00:18:52,599
Apprentices teach more apprentices

376
00:18:52,679 --> 00:18:53,679
And open more branches

377
00:18:54,359 --> 00:18:56,320
When branches are blossoming everywhere

378
00:18:56,639 --> 00:18:58,399
You'll be the Grandmaster

379
00:18:59,119 --> 00:18:59,919
As the Grandmaster

380
00:18:59,919 --> 00:19:02,080
You'll just lie at home counting money every day

381
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:05,960
Who is this distinguished expert?

382
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,399
I am Xuanjizi

383
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:08,879
Well said

384
00:19:09,879 --> 00:19:11,040
Well said

385
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:14,000
I thought only hotpot could make money

386
00:19:14,359 --> 00:19:15,679
After hearing you say that

387
00:19:16,159 --> 00:19:18,040
My vision was a bit narrow

388
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:19,960
Not at all, not at all

389
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,599
I don't want to be any Grandmaster

390
00:19:21,919 --> 00:19:23,520
Nor do I want to make money

391
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:24,839
Don't talk nonsense

392
00:19:25,199 --> 00:19:26,800
Money is a good thing

393
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:27,599
Exactly

394
00:19:27,679 --> 00:19:29,040
If not for money, what are you doing this for?

395
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,040
I'm doing it to

396
00:19:30,879 --> 00:19:32,720
Take down the bully across the street

397
00:19:34,159 --> 00:19:34,599
Bully?

398
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:35,439
Over there

399
00:19:40,679 --> 00:19:42,280
That's a pretty lofty ambition.

400
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:44,119
But you're running on nothing but passion.

401
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:45,080
You've got no bullets.

402
00:19:45,399 --> 00:19:45,919
How can you fight?

403
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:47,879
Exactly, exactly.

404
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:50,679
Money is what gives you a backbone.

405
00:19:50,679 --> 00:19:52,199
We can do both.

406
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:54,000
Right, right.

407
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:55,879
Let's do it together.

408
00:19:56,359 --> 00:19:57,080
Together, together.

409
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:58,760
Open a branch, open a branch.

410
00:19:58,919 --> 00:20:00,000
We can open a branch.

411
00:20:05,919 --> 00:20:08,000
The bully is right across the street.

412
00:20:12,439 --> 00:20:14,159
Help me dig into their lair.

413
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,080
Then I'll have time to teach apprentices.

414
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:18,639
That's the only way to fulfill...

415
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,480
...your dream of making easy money.

416
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,080
No problem, no problem.

417
00:20:31,919 --> 00:20:32,439
Together.

418
00:20:33,560 --> 00:20:34,679
We're all in this together.

419
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:57,439
Did we dig in the wrong direction?

420
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,839
Impossible.

421
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:01,760
I know that underneath their house...

422
00:21:02,159 --> 00:21:04,240
...there is a cellar for tea...

423
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,639
...and a tunnel to escape disaster.

424
00:21:06,879 --> 00:21:09,280
We just need to dig through to their tunnel...

425
00:21:09,839 --> 00:21:10,919
...and we'll be through.

426
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:22,679
Even if they have a tunnel,

427
00:21:23,119 --> 00:21:24,800
the tunnel should be under the courtyard.

428
00:21:25,599 --> 00:21:27,679
Their courtyard should be in that direction.

429
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:30,919
Impossible.

430
00:21:31,320 --> 00:21:33,480
I think it's right here.

431
00:21:34,359 --> 00:21:35,320
Is your guess even accurate?

432
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:36,800
Or is my compass more accurate?

433
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:38,439
If we dig wrong, it's all for nothing.

434
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:40,439
Trust me.

435
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:41,919
This is my trade.

436
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,359
You help out too.

437
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:49,000
I provide the brains, you provide the brawn.

438
00:21:49,199 --> 00:21:50,119
Fair and square.

439
00:21:50,439 --> 00:21:51,000
You...

440
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,399
What's the situation up ahead?

441
00:21:55,800 --> 00:21:56,800
Queuing for hotpot.

442
00:21:56,879 --> 00:21:57,679
Hotpot?

443
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,560
Hotpot is so unrefined.

444
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:00,480
What's so good about it?

445
00:22:00,839 --> 00:22:01,599
I find it strange too.

446
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:03,560
But there are so many people eating there every day.

447
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:04,919
I'll clear the place immediately.

448
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:07,040
Clear out, clear out, clear out!

449
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:07,839
Go, go, go!

450
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:09,040
Clear out, clear out, clear out!

451
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:12,879
Dongshihui.

452
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:13,919
Stop.

453
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:21,240
Two days ago, this Young Master Huo sent gifts.

454
00:22:21,439 --> 00:22:23,520
Asking me to arrest the boss of Dongshihui.

455
00:22:24,599 --> 00:22:26,520
It seems this Dongshihui boss...

456
00:22:26,639 --> 00:22:28,040
...is quite something.

457
00:22:28,839 --> 00:22:29,639
Move it, move it.

458
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,520
Move it.

459
00:22:33,919 --> 00:22:34,480
Where is everyone?

460
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:35,599
Why is it all...

461
00:22:38,439 --> 00:22:40,280
A distinguished guest has arrived.

462
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:41,760
Clear the tables.

463
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:42,399
Please sit.

464
00:22:42,399 --> 00:22:43,040
Please, please.

465
00:22:43,599 --> 00:22:44,599
Sit, sit, sit.

466
00:22:46,159 --> 00:22:47,480
A tiny hotpot shop.

467
00:22:47,879 --> 00:22:49,480
Looks pretty ordinary to me.

468
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:51,040
What signature dishes do you have?

469
00:22:51,399 --> 00:22:52,080
Our shop...

470
00:22:52,520 --> 00:22:55,240
Every dish is a signature dish.

471
00:22:55,839 --> 00:22:57,080
A toad yawning...

472
00:22:57,080 --> 00:22:58,040
What big talk.

473
00:22:58,359 --> 00:22:59,599
Then bring a bit of everything.

474
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:00,439
Alright!

475
00:23:00,599 --> 00:23:03,320
A bit of every specialty in the house!

476
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:05,399
Go personally.

477
00:23:07,599 --> 00:23:09,080
Commander Qin.

478
00:23:09,199 --> 00:23:10,280
Your distinguished presence...

479
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:11,800
Why didn't you tell me?

480
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:13,560
I just stopped by for a hotpot.

481
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,879
No need to disturb Young Master Huo.

482
00:23:16,599 --> 00:23:17,399
This kind of fly-infested joint...

483
00:23:17,399 --> 00:23:19,439
Surely can't catch Commander Qin's eye.

484
00:23:20,080 --> 00:23:21,320
I invite Commander Qin...

485
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:22,960
...to my home for a sit-down.

486
00:23:23,280 --> 00:23:26,240
I'll have my chef prepare a good meal for Commander Qin.

487
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:28,320
Flies or mosquitoes, it's all meat.

488
00:23:28,599 --> 00:23:30,080
I came here for its reputation.

489
00:23:30,320 --> 00:23:31,720
Here it comes!

490
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:36,240
Dongshihui's authentic spicy hotpot!

491
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:40,320
What are you doing here?

492
00:23:40,839 --> 00:23:42,040
We don't welcome you here.

493
00:23:42,919 --> 00:23:46,280
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

494
00:23:46,839 --> 00:23:49,960
Come out, come out, let Xiugu come out!

495
00:23:50,839 --> 00:23:51,560
Commander Qin.

496
00:23:51,879 --> 00:23:53,919
This is the scoundrel I told you about.

497
00:23:54,119 --> 00:23:55,399
To steal my woman...

498
00:23:55,520 --> 00:23:57,960
He opened this fly-infested joint right at my doorstep.

499
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,399
Spying on me every day.

500
00:23:59,679 --> 00:24:00,159
Just look.

501
00:24:00,359 --> 00:24:01,760
Giving my household no peace.

502
00:24:02,399 --> 00:24:03,639
I request Commander Qin...

503
00:24:03,919 --> 00:24:05,679
...to purge this peace-disturbing...

504
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:06,760
...lawless element.

505
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:09,800
Commander Qin...

506
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:14,080
The parent official of the local people.

507
00:24:14,159 --> 00:24:15,720
A good official!

508
00:24:16,040 --> 00:24:17,359
I want to report a crime too.

509
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:21,240
This man kidnapped a decent woman.

510
00:24:21,439 --> 00:24:24,199
That is the wife I married with a grand sedan chair.

511
00:24:24,879 --> 00:24:26,839
You can't have her, so you slander me here.

512
00:24:27,439 --> 00:24:28,800
Ever since she went in...

513
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:30,960
No sign of her, alive or dead.

514
00:24:31,159 --> 00:24:32,320
Call her out.

515
00:24:32,599 --> 00:24:33,639
Let's confront her face-to-face.

516
00:24:34,760 --> 00:24:35,240
Right.

517
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:36,800
I came to eat hotpot.

518
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:37,800
You're making such a racket.

519
00:24:38,040 --> 00:24:39,320
Whatever it is, sit down and talk.

520
00:24:39,679 --> 00:24:40,159
Sit.

521
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:41,080
Fine, sit.

522
00:24:42,359 --> 00:24:43,199
Come, come, come.

523
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,119
Talk while we eat.

524
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:52,199
This hotpot tastes really good.

525
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:56,080
I think your business is going to get bigger and bigger.

526
00:24:56,320 --> 00:24:57,480
Once the business gets big,

527
00:24:58,599 --> 00:25:00,760
do you need this officer to do anything for you?

528
00:25:01,119 --> 00:25:02,000
Yes, yes.

529
00:25:02,199 --> 00:25:03,919
Tell that bastard to release Xiu Gu.

530
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:05,399
Xiu Gu?

531
00:25:06,119 --> 00:25:07,599
Xiu Gu is our young mistress.

532
00:25:07,879 --> 00:25:09,040
Is her name something you can just shout out?

533
00:25:10,280 --> 00:25:10,839
Right.

534
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,439
We are all men who do big things.

535
00:25:14,800 --> 00:25:16,679
Why get so caught up in romance?

536
00:25:17,359 --> 00:25:18,520
Commander Qin.

537
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:22,080
This shop was opened for Xiu Gu.

538
00:25:22,280 --> 00:25:23,560
If Xiu Gu isn't here,

539
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:26,159
this shop has no meaning at all.

540
00:25:26,839 --> 00:25:27,839
So you mean...

541
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:30,119
Xiu Gu is your shop's treasure?

542
00:25:33,199 --> 00:25:35,520
Then just give Xiu Gu back to them.

543
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:37,359
You can just marry another one.

544
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,720
Marry three, I'll be the matchmaker.

545
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:42,000
Commander Qin.

546
00:25:42,639 --> 00:25:45,119
You're making things difficult for me.

547
00:25:46,599 --> 00:25:48,080
Otherwise, what did you think?

548
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:52,639
What's going on? Don't wreck the place.

549
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,480
Easy, easy, easy.

550
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:57,599
What?

551
00:25:58,639 --> 00:26:00,199
We are...

552
00:26:00,439 --> 00:26:01,599
Reno... renovating.

553
00:26:08,119 --> 00:26:08,800
Commander Qin.

554
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:13,280
Renovations are loud, might spoil your appetite a bit.

555
00:26:13,399 --> 00:26:14,040
How about this?

556
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:17,080
I'll pack it up and deliver it to your door later.

557
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:18,040
What is "packing it up"?

558
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:18,960
"Packing it up" means...

559
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:21,839
pot, stove, and all the dishes,

560
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:24,560
all packed up and delivered to your residence.

561
00:26:25,159 --> 00:26:27,879
This meal is my tribute to Commander Qin.

562
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:30,639
Sensible.

563
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:35,359
You should be sensible too.

564
00:26:37,879 --> 00:26:38,919
I have high hopes for you.

565
00:26:45,280 --> 00:26:47,480
Farewell, Commander Qin.

566
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,040
Up!

567
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:03,480
She's truly a dwarf crossing a river—dead set on it.

568
00:27:04,359 --> 00:27:05,960
She hasn't eaten or drunk anything for days.

569
00:27:07,399 --> 00:27:09,080
She fainted several times in between.

570
00:27:10,159 --> 00:27:11,280
I told Mama Zhang to forcibly...

571
00:27:11,280 --> 00:27:12,919
pour some sugar water down her throat.

572
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:14,800
Just to keep her alive.

573
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:17,560
This can't go on like this.

574
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:22,679
I'm afraid... someone might really die.

575
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,720
This is the spot.

576
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:41,839
The height is right too.

577
00:27:42,359 --> 00:27:43,839
Come on, who's doing the final poke?

578
00:27:43,839 --> 00:27:44,599
Me, me.

579
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:48,520
Poked it.

580
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:49,159
Let there be light!

581
00:27:59,560 --> 00:28:00,720
How come I see the sky?

582
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:03,879
I don't see a house.

583
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:06,280
I told you your direction was wrong.

584
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:07,919
The compass can't be wrong.

585
00:28:09,359 --> 00:28:10,639
This should be the back garden.

586
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,639
Listen, there are birds chirping.

587
00:28:14,599 --> 00:28:15,599
Here, let me go up first.

588
00:28:15,599 --> 00:28:16,199
Come, come, come.

589
00:28:16,399 --> 00:28:17,000
Stand on this.

590
00:28:17,199 --> 00:28:17,720
Come, come, come.

591
00:28:19,359 --> 00:28:20,159
Easy, easy.

592
00:28:20,599 --> 00:28:21,080
Up.

593
00:28:21,439 --> 00:28:21,919
Up.

594
00:28:25,119 --> 00:28:27,280
This is a garden, it is a garden.

595
00:28:31,159 --> 00:28:32,119
The direction is right.

596
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:34,839
Why is there a wall?

597
00:28:37,679 --> 00:28:38,599
Garden...

598
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,800
Do you see that?

599
00:28:40,599 --> 00:28:41,919
Dongshihui.

600
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:53,080
The direction was dug correctly,

601
00:28:53,879 --> 00:28:56,800
but the distance is way off.

602
00:29:07,199 --> 00:29:09,159
What are you guys doing here?

603
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,119
We...

604
00:29:12,119 --> 00:29:12,639
We...

605
00:29:14,080 --> 00:29:14,720
We...

606
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:15,839
Playing hide-and-seek.

607
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:18,639
Caught you.

608
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:20,000
I caught you too.

609
00:29:20,439 --> 00:29:22,439
You come catch me.

610
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,280
Didn't you want Xiu Gu?

611
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:29,520
Bring her over.

612
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:35,800
Come.

613
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:37,040
Returning her to you.

614
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:47,359
Did the Huo family not feed you?

615
00:29:49,439 --> 00:29:50,720
Don't mention the Huo family ever again.

616
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,359
I went on a hunger strike myself.

617
00:29:54,119 --> 00:29:55,879
I didn't expect that as soon as I got out,

618
00:29:55,879 --> 00:29:57,119
you guys would have opened a hotpot restaurant.

619
00:29:58,439 --> 00:29:59,399
And doing so well too.

620
00:30:12,599 --> 00:30:14,119
Just look at this hand.

621
00:30:14,280 --> 00:30:15,399
Just take a look.

622
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:17,199
Look at this hand.

623
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:21,480
Look how he tortured you.

624
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:25,599
That bastard, Huo.

625
00:30:26,399 --> 00:30:27,639
I'm going to settle the score with him.

626
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:29,280
What score can you settle on your own?

627
00:30:32,599 --> 00:30:33,159
Xiao Fan

628
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:36,960
Let's just let this matter go.

629
00:30:37,399 --> 00:30:40,439
Young Master Huo caught you then let you go.

630
00:30:40,679 --> 00:30:42,359
What exactly is his game?

631
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,399
I can't help but feel...

632
00:30:44,679 --> 00:30:46,800
...he's plotting some scheme behind our backs.

633
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:49,040
We're on the same wavelength.

634
00:30:49,800 --> 00:30:51,000
We thought the exact same thing.

635
00:30:52,639 --> 00:30:53,639
This guy named Huo...

636
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:54,960
I wonder...

637
00:30:56,159 --> 00:30:58,040
The King of Hell's wife is pregnant.

638
00:30:59,080 --> 00:31:00,760
What devilish scheme is he brewing?

639
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:03,560
I don't care what devilish scheme he's brewing.

640
00:31:03,839 --> 00:31:05,679
I'm going to fight him to the end.

641
00:31:05,679 --> 00:31:06,599
Dad

642
00:31:08,199 --> 00:31:09,960
Cutting ties with the Huo family...

643
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,439
...is a good thing.

644
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:14,520
All I want now is...

645
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:17,639
...to live a peaceful life.

